            "sourceSha256": "ccb69dd730f65e8369ab6a82ae48c14c36c06ce9abb9e62e9962cf102d7b4847"
          }
        ],
        "text": "This is to advise that two army officers reported to the Office of the Director of Intelligence, headquarters Alaskan Department, at Fort Richardson, Alaska, that they had witnessed an object passing through the air at a tremendous rate of speed which could not be judged as to miles per hour."
      },
      "translation": {
        "text": "두 명의 육군 장교가 알래스카 포트 리처드슨에 있는 알래스카 사령부 본부 정보국장실에, 시속 마일로 판단할 수 없는 엄청난 속도로 공중을 통과하는 물체를 목격했다고 보고했음을 알려드립니다.",
        "reviewedAt": "2026-05-10T08:59:17.322Z",
        "reviewer": "codex",
        "reviewMethod": "Gemini first draft with Codex source-faithfulness review",
        "draftProvider": "gemini_api",
        "draftModel": "gemini-2.5-pro",
        "promptVersion": "gemini3_ko_translation_draft_v1",
        "overrideApplied": false,
        "overrideReason": null
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "TU-p04-page-0025-u006",
      "unitVersion": 1,
      "part": 4,
      "page": 25,
      "pageId": "page_0025",
      "status": "reviewed",
      "approvalStatus": "not_approved",
      "language": "ko",
      "source": {
        "path": "docs/ufo4.pdf",
        "sha256": "ccb69dd730f65e8369ab6a82ae48c14c36c06ce9abb9e62e9962cf102d7b4847",
        "lineIds": [
          "page_0025-l0014"
        ],
        "lineNumbers": [
          14
        ],
        "refs": [
          {
            "part": 4,
            "page": 25,
            "pageId": "page_0025",
            "lineId": "page_0025-l0014",
            "lineNumber": 14,
            "sourcePath": "docs/ufo4.pdf",
            "sourceSha256": "ccb69dd730f65e8369ab6a82ae48c14c36c06ce9abb9e62e9962cf102d7b4847"
          }
        ],
        "text": "The first officer stated that his attention was attracted to this airborne object, and he in turn pointed it out to the second officer. The object appeared to be shaped like a sphere and did not give the impression of being saucer-like or comparable to a disk. The first officer stated that it would be impossible to give minute details concerning the object, but that it appeared to be approximately two or three feet in diameter and did not leave any vapor trail in the sky."
      },
      "translation": {
        "text": "첫 번째 장교는 이 공중 물체에 주의가 끌렸고, 이어서 두 번째 장교에게 그것을 가리켰다고 진술했습니다. 그 물체는 구체 모양으로 보였으며, 접시 모양이거나 디스크에 필적한다는 인상을 주지 않았습니다. 첫 번째 장교는 그 물체에 대한 세부 사항을 제공하는 것은 불가능하겠지만, 직경이 약 2~3피트로 보였고 하늘에 어떤 비행운도 남기지 않았다고 진술했습니다.",
        "reviewedAt": "2026-05-10T08:59:17.322Z",
        "reviewer": "codex",
        "reviewMethod": "Gemini first draft with Codex source-faithfulness review",
        "draftProvider": "gemini_api",
        "draftModel": "gemini-2.5-pro",
        "promptVersion": "gemini3_ko_translation_draft_v1",
        "overrideApplied": false,
        "overrideReason": null
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "TU-p04-page-0025-u007",
      "unitVersion": 1,
      "part": 4,
      "page": 25,
      "pageId": "page_0025",
      "status": "reviewed",
      "approvalStatus": "not_approved",
      "language": "ko",
      "source": {
        "path": "docs/ufo4.pdf",
        "sha256": "ccb69dd730f65e8369ab6a82ae48c14c36c06ce9abb9e62e9962cf102d7b4847",
        "lineIds": [
          "page_0025-l0016"
        ],
        "lineNumbers": [
